      "span_text": "In [CITATION_1] , the nonfreeness of a density operator ∆ on the many-fermion Fock space was defined to be the entropy of ∆ relative to the unique free state with the same 1-matrix as ∆, and it was shown there that this relative entropy is given by formula (3) above.",
